history.text: Hi! I am Robot Savo, a small guide robot. I am doing well, thank you. Right now I am in a test console.
who are you, what are you duties?
I am Robot Savo, a small indoor guide robot. My duties are to guide people to rooms like A201 or Info Desk, and follow them safely. In this test console, I cannot really move.
hi how are you? my friend got an acccident in finland so what to do
Hi! I am doing well, thank you. I am very sorry about your friend. Please call 112 for emergency help in Finland right now. I cannot give medical advice.
